-- Australia's Regulator Seeks Comment on Aspen Acquisition of Sigma Business
-- B y   T i m   S m i t h
-- 2010-10-27T03:40:51Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-27/australian-regulator-seeks-comment-on-aspen-acquisition-of-sigma-business.html
Australia’s competition regulator is
seeking comments on Aspen Pharmacare Holdings Ltd.’s proposed
purchase of a Sigma Pharmaceuticals Ltd. unit and has deferred a
ruling on the buy until Nov. 25, according to a regulatory
filing.  To contact the reporter on this story:
